14:26.315 --> 14:34.023
able to come to, let's say, people like Martin 
Johnson and talk about your problems, many

14:26.315 --> 14:34.023
meetings, this sort of thing? Not particularly. 
As far as the kind of research work was concerned,

14:38.138 --> 14:57.306
everybody did their own particular job, but as I 
mentioned a few minutes ago, we did collect

14:38.138 --> 14:57.306
plankton samples on these cruises. The 
phytoplankton were examined by Mr. Allen and His

15:05.645 --> 15:18.282
associate, Easter Kopp, and Mark Johnson and his 
assistants and students did the work on the

15:05.645 --> 15:18.282
zooplankton. So, yes, and the group was small 
