optimize what we could do, because we had very

23:00.743 --> 23:07.314
limited resources in terms of money and people and 
equipment. So we had to select fairly carefully

23:07.374 --> 23:13.183
what we felt we could do. I have to remember that 
most of this was even before the days of the whole

