27:10.821 --> 27:13.225
Scripps at that time. This is after the Blue Fin. 
We're getting in a number of omissions and so on in

27:15.267 --> 27:24.260
trying to trace the history of these things. But we 
were all, we were not We did not consider, as one

27:29.292 --> 27:36.101
would probably do now that we were dependent on 
federal funding to function. We were essentially

27:36.241 --> 27:45.934
supported through the academic funds from the 
University of California.

27:46.655 --> 27:54.625
There was also support from some of the members of 
the Scripps family, which was available at that

27:46.655 --> 27:54.625
time. There has also been discussion that perhaps 
the nature of oceanography has changed for the

27:55.870 --> 28:04.640
worse and that they have lost sort of a 
jack-of-all-trades approach. Would you agree

28:04.660 --> 28:05.441
with that? Well, this is, I think, where personal 
prejudice has come in, and I would agree that I feel

28:05.982 --> 28:22.401
that one of the things that attracted me to the 
field originally was the fact that we were able to

28:05.982 --> 28:22.401
deal with a what I consider is essentially a sort of 
a unified system, and where we could cross the

28:22.972 --> 28:45.141
disciplinary boundaries, which we did very 
freely at that time, between chemistry, physical

28:22.972 --> 28:45.141
aspects, biology, geology, without anybody 
raising an eyebrow. And we did try and deal with the

28:45.662 --> 28:49.367
systems well as we could as essentially unified 
systems. And I think today it's become fragmented

28:54.530 --> 29:15.135
again by specialization, which is partly, I 
think, the result of the interest of the

28:54.530 --> 29:15.135
scientists who come into the field, but it's also 
being encouraged in a sense, by the way in which the

29:15.875 --> 29:24.491
federal funding has become more and more 
specialized and fragmented. And I don't consider

29:25.834 --> 29:30.242
this desirable at all. Most of my efforts in recent 
years have been to try and bring the subject matter

29:30.963 --> 29:38.457
back together again as much as I can.

